        Selling in Gumdale 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Gumdale's acreage holdings, equestrian-friendly blocks and semi-rural character within the Brisbane city limits attract a smaller but highly specific buyer pool. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
